            name: "Restaurant Patio",
            desc: "The patio overlooks nothing in particular—just an endless starfield gently swirling beyond a transparent force field. A few metal tables are bolted to the floor, but nicely appointed with linens and decorative centerpieces. There is a sign by the edge of the balcony.",
