        (
            id: "poetry-panic",
            name: "Bad Poetry Panic Room",
            desc: "A concrete and titanium vacuum-sealed room equipped with noise generators, active voice-cancelling harmonics and Cone of Silence™ technology. Faint mist drifts from a ceiling vent next to a very large [[b]]scorch mark[[/b]]. A seal on the wall proudly boasts that the chamber is [[i]][[b]]almost[[/b]][[/i]] completely Vogon poetry-proof.",
