            id: "inca-road",
            name: "Inca Road",
            desc: "An ancient road of broken and uneven stones winds precariously along the mountainside, half-swallowed by time and weeds. Across the road lies a trim, modern lawn with an improbably square footprint. Oddly, the pristene green grass leads right up to the loading dock of a squat commercial building that seems to have landed here by accident. A [[item]]welcome sign[[/item]] looms large next to the road at the edge of the lawn.",
