            id: "med-bay",
            name: "Med Bay",
            desc: "A clean white infirmary with two bio-beds extending from the back wall, surrounded by a bevy of monitors and robotic surgical tools. One of the machines goes \"Bing!\" every few minutes. A small cleaning robot floats around the room disinfecting things. A large, [[b]]lit red button[[/b]] is set into the wall between the beds.",
