        ),
        (
            id: "shoe_propaganda",
            name: "Tract of The Shoe",
            desc: "A brief and hastily printed religious pamphlet entitled [[i]]The Sole for your Soul.[[/i]]",
            movability: free,
            container_state: None,
            location: Item("jackson_mailbox"),
            visibility: listed,
            visible_when: Some(Pred(hasFlag(
                flag: "sect-shoe",
            ))),
            aliases: [
                "pamphlet",
            ],
            abilities: [
                read,
            ],
            interaction_requires: {},
            text: Some("\n    [[box]][[hl]]THE SOLE FOR YOUR SOUL[[/hl]][[/box]]\n\n    Have you considered the Shoe?\n\n    For generations the misguided have followed the Gourd,\n    a vegetable of questionable theological stability.\n    But the Shoe is firm, dependable, and already prepared\n    for walking the Path.\n\n    [[center]][[hl]]Why the Shoe?[[/hl]][[/center]]\n\n    • The Shoe protects the faithful from sharp stones.\n    • The Shoe has a clear left and right doctrine.\n    • The Shoe leaves footprints for others to follow.\n\n    [[center]][[hl]]Common Heresy[[/hl]][[/center]]\n\n    Some claim the Gourd represents nourishment.\n    This is clearly false. One cannot walk upon a gourd,\n    nor can one tie it securely. Honestly, it would\n    be easier to eat a shoe. And tastier.\n\n    [[center]][[hl]]A MESSAGE TO THE UNDECIDED[[/hl]][[/center]]\n\n    If the Shoe fits, wear it.\n\n    Followers of the Shoe meet every third Thursday\n    behind the Parish of St. Alfonzo (weather permitting).\n\n    Remember:\n    [[i]]Blessed are the semi-shod, for they shall hop the Path.[[/i]]\n"),
            consumable: None,
        ),
        (
            id: "gourdies_out_sign",
            name: "Tiny Billboard",
            desc: "A tiny metal billboard, planted at a slight angle into the mulch around the base of the much larger welcome sign.",
            movability: fixed(
                reason: "Heresy! As a Follower of the Shoe, you must let this sign stand.",
            ),
            container_state: None,
            location: Room("inca-road"),
            visibility: scenery,
            visible_when: Some(Pred(hasFlag(
                flag: "sect-shoe",
            ))),
            aliases: [],
            abilities: [
                read,
            ],
            interaction_requires: {},
            text: Some("[[center]]AUTHORIZED FOOTWEAR ZONE[[/center]][[center]]— Gourdites Keep Out![[/center]]"),
            consumable: None,
        ),
        (
            id: "shoe_pamphlet",
            name: "Worn Pamphlet",
            desc: "A newly printed pamphlet, advertising a narrow selection of simple sandals — but only the [[u]]left[[/u]] ones, \"[[i]]For the discerning Follower of the Shoe[[/i]]\"",
            movability: free,
            container_state: None,
            location: Room("lounge"),
            visibility: listed,
            visible_when: Some(Pred(hasFlag(
                flag: "sect-shoe",
            ))),
            aliases: [],
            abilities: [
                read,
            ],
            interaction_requires: {},
            text: Some("[[i]]Printed on flame-retardant sheets from Initech™[[/i]]"),
            consumable: None,
        ),
        (
            id: "gourd_propaganda",
            name: "Tract of The Gourd",
            desc: "A brief and hastily printed religious pamphlet entitled [[i]]The Gourd from the Lord.[[/i]]",
            movability: free,
            container_state: None,
            location: Item("jackson_mailbox"),
            visibility: listed,
            visible_when: Some(Pred(hasFlag(
                flag: "sect-gourd",
            ))),
            aliases: [
                "pamphlet",
            ],
            abilities: [
                read,
            ],
            interaction_requires: {},
            text: Some("\n    [[box]][[hl]]THE GOURD FROM OUR LORD[[/hl]][[/box]]\n\n    Friends, have you heard the Gospel of the Gourd?\n\n    While misguided sects worship shoddy unilateral footwear,\n    the Gourd offers something far greater:\n    spiritual nourishment and seasonal availability.\n\n    [[center]][[hl]]Why the Gourd?[[/hl]][[/center]]\n\n    • The Gourd grows naturally from the Earth.\n    • The Gourd contains many seeds of wisdom.\n    • The Gourd cannot accidentally be worn on the wrong foot.\n\n    [[center]][[hl]]A WARNING[[/hl]][[/center]]\n\n    The followers of the Shoe claim their object\n    \"supports the faithful.\"\n\n    This is clearly ridiculous. Shoes merely follow\n    wherever people go.\n\n    The Gourd leads.\n\n    [[center]][[hl]]A MESSAGE TO THE CURIOUS[[/hl]][[/center]]\n\n    Take up the Gourd and rejoice!\n\n    Meetings of the Faithful of the Gourd occur\n    whenever enough people remember to show up with one.\n\n    Remember:\n    [[i]]Your Soul Cannot Afford the Absence of Gourd[[/i]]\n"),
            consumable: None,
        ),
        (
            id: "gourd_meeting_note",
            name: "Gourder Meeting Memo",
            desc: "A handwritten memo to the [[i]][[b]]Followers of the Gourd[[/b]][[/i]] found tacked to the St. Alfonzo\'s sign.",
